e present some results from a detector before and after\ndeposition of an isolated steering grid. The grid indeed improves on the\ndetectors energy resolution and detection efficiency. We show that simulations\ncan be used to model the anode to cathode charge correlation in excellent\nagreement with the experimental results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Aug 2006 17:42:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
